                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "It explores the ‘how’, ‘why’ and ‘what if’.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "What is most important \/ interesting \/ useful \/ relevant about the object, event, experience or idea? (TOPIC)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
