                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Imagine a wide-angle lens looking out over your scene. Introduce the place\/person.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Zoom in on one particular place, aspect of a person, a scene. Describe in vivid detail what you have zoomed in on (5 senses, descriptive language, literary language). End the paragraph with something you can link to the next paragraph.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Focus on another aspect of the person\/place\/object. End the paragraph with something you can link to the next paragraph.",
